That virtual graduation was so miserable, but these memories are coming back, my favorite school years would have to be 2015 - 2016 (Kindergarten), 2016 - 2017 (First Grade), and 2017 - 2018 (Second Grade), mainly because all of my teachers gave me best memories of my life/childhood and most of my friend group started from here.
